      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "To elevate this for *Nature*, you need stronger verbs and a more definitive claim. Consider revising it to highlight the fundamental implications rather than just the suggestion of limitations. For example, something like: \"We systematically mapped the cognitive frontiers of large language models using rigorous psychometric testing. Our results quantitatively delineate critical failure modes in high-order reasoning, fundamentally constraining present-day neural network architectures. This work offers a vital empirical scaffold for guiding the next generation of artificial general intelligence research.\"",
